    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes a lot of sense. It feels like those mandates are basically written for people who don't understand how a small town actually works. On the flip side, what do the people pushing for these hikes actually say is the benefit? Is there any real economic argument there or is it just about the optics?",
